ort back to the House including a minority report explaining the delays to date?</p><p class="Interjection"><strong>Mr SPEAKER</strong>: Scott Simpson can answer the question.</p><p class="SupAnswer"><strong>SCOTT SIMPSON</strong>: The select committee continues its work on the bill and has yet to complete that work. I am not at liberty under the Standing Orders to delve into the detail of our work before it reports back to the House.</p><p class="QOAEnd"><a name="time_20161103 15:10:05 " ></a><strong> </strong></p></div></body>
